@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Welcome!";
}
@section featured {
    <div class="page-header" id="banner">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h1>@ViewBag.Title</h1>
                <p class="lead">@ViewBag.Message</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
}
<div ng-app>
    <div class="col-lg-8">
        <h2>Before we begin:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <h3>Resources</h3>
                In the main menu, you will find important resources to help you out with this lab. The meaning of this lab is not only to show you what is possible when using Octopus Deploy, but it's also for you to do some reading and searching for solutions on your own. So take a quick look at the resources found in the main menu!
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Exercises</h3>
                You will find several exercises in this lab. Some require coding whilst other require you to look at code and see if you can understand what is going on. In other words, you will be extending this website on your own. Fun, fun, fun!
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Need help?</h3>
                Feel free to contact me on <a href="http://www.twitter.com/karolikl">Twitter</a>.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="panel panel-primary">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title">The exercise box</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                Whenever you see one of these boxes, there is an exercise for you to do.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-info">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title">The information box</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                The information box contains useful information and links to resources that can help you out.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <div>
                <p>
                    @Html.ActionLink("Let's begin!", "Server", "Installation", null, new { @class = "btn btn-primary right" })
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
